Object-Extend version 0.0.1
==========================

This module allows Ruby (and JavaScript) style "singleton methods" to be added to Perl objects. Singleton methods are added to an object-specific class (the object's C<eigenclass>) which extends the object's original class. The original class is left unchanged.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  Test::More

